- Composite snapshots misclassified as single frame (current example is composite).
- Duplicate figlet text causes restore ambiguity (loader matches by text only in figlet restore path, `app/wwdos_app.cpp:3688`).
- Timeline has one-primer limit; workspaces can have multiple `frame_player` windows.
- Figlet size drift if converting from semantic timeline and recomputing bounds (`preview_figlet`) under different font/chrome settings.
- `/state` vs workspace schema drift if props are added to one but not the other.

